# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# TRADING COMPETITION BOT — Environment Variables
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values
# NEVER commit .env to git

# ── Discord ──────────────────────────────────────────────
DISCORD_TOKEN=your_bot_token_here
DISCORD_CLIENT_ID=your_application_id_here
GUILD_ID=your_server_id_here          # Dev guild for instant slash command reload

# ── Database ─────────────────────────────────────────────
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/trading_bot
DB_POOL_MIN=2
DB_POOL_MAX=10

# ── Redis ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379
REDIS_TTL_LEADERBOARD=300             # Cache leaderboard 5 minutes
REDIS_TTL_SESSION=3600                # Sessions 1 hour

# ── Security ─────────────────────────────────────────────
AES_SECRET_KEY=32_character_secret_key_here_!!  # Exactly 32 chars for AES-256
JWT_SECRET=another_random_secret_for_sessions

# ── MetaApi (MT4/MT5 bridge) ─────────────────────────────
METAAPI_TOKEN=your_metaapi_token_here
METAAPI_POLL_INTERVAL_MINUTES=15      # Polling frequency per account

# ── Express HTTP Server (for EA webhook) ─────────────────
HTTP_PORT=3000
HTTP_SECRET=secret_token_for_ea_webhook   # Shared secret between EA and bot

# ── Scoring Weights ───────────────────────────────────────
WEIGHT_PNL=0.4
WEIGHT_WINRATE=0.3
WEIGHT_DRAWDOWN=0.2
WEIGHT_CONSISTENCY=0.1

# ── Leaderboard Tiers ────────────────────────────────────
BRONZE_MIN_SCORE=0
SILVER_MIN_SCORE=500
GOLD_PROMO_PCT=20      # Top 20% of Gold gets promoted
PLAT_PROMO_PCT=15
DIAMOND_PROMO_PCT=10
APEX_PROMO_PCT=5

# ── Invite Gate ───────────────────────────────────────────
INVITE_REQUIRED_COUNT=2         # How many active invites needed
INVITE_ACTIVE_HOURS=24          # Hours an invite must be active to count

# ── Roles (fill after creating roles in Discord) ─────────
ROLE_VERIFIED_TRADER=role_id_here
ROLE_BRONZE=role_id_here
ROLE_SILVER=role_id_here
ROLE_GOLD=role_id_here
ROLE_PLATINUM=role_id_here
ROLE_DIAMOND=role_id_here
ROLE_APEX=role_id_here
ROLE_ADMIN=role_id_here

# ── Channels ──────────────────────────────────────────────
CHANNEL_ANNOUNCEMENTS=channel_id_here
CHANNEL_LEADERBOARD=channel_id_here
CHANNEL_BATTLES=channel_id_here

# ── Environment ───────────────────────────────────────────
NODE_ENV=development              # development | production
LOG_LEVEL=info                    # debug | info | warn | error
SENTRY_DSN=                       # Optional: Sentry error tracking
